              "body": "Non-native speaker question: is \u201cmitigate against something\u201d or \u201cmitigate something\u201d?  (In Italian, \u201cmitigate\u201d does not require any proposition because it is a transitive verb.)",
              "createdAt": "2025-04-07T10:17:49Z",
