              "originalPosition": 67,
              "body": "Maybe we can be more specific.  (The `?` in the ref implicitly makes an \u201cinformational reference\u201d entry.  However, we probably want to be consistent with the current model \u2014 i.e., being explicit.)\r\n\r\n```suggestion\r\nAn example of this is caching in HTTP {{?STD98}} and CoAP {{?RFC7252}}.\r\n```",
